<ENAMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">Firstly</ENAMEX> , in order to do well in the work of reducing and eliminating outdated spindles , subsidies of <ENAMEX TYPE="MONEY">3 million yuan</ENAMEX> will be granted for every <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">10,000</ENAMEX> spindles reduced .
