<ENAMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">Secondly</ENAMEX> , in <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">1998</ENAMEX> , the reserve fund for bad bank debts to be cancelled with the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">State</ENAMEX> approval will lean heavily towards the textile industry .
